WEBVTT

00:11.400 --> 00:14.130
Do you still remember
the day I left for Great Yan?

00:15.000 --> 00:16.000
You told me

00:17.390 --> 00:18.550
you needed me.

00:19.760 --> 00:20.800
Now,

00:21.190 --> 00:22.070
Zhuge Yue,

00:23.320 --> 00:24.890
can you stay for me?

01:00.880 --> 01:01.520
Qiao!

01:10.789 --> 01:11.510
Qiao!

01:27.230 --> 01:27.840
Qiao...

01:29.070 --> 01:30.000
You're injured.

01:31.870 --> 01:32.729
What happened?

01:33.710 --> 01:34.840
How did you get hurt?

01:35.050 --> 01:35.640
Li Ce.

01:38.470 --> 01:39.530
My eyes are healed.

02:59.040 --> 03:04.540
[REBIRTH]

03:05.030 --> 03:07.500
[Episode 7]

03:07.570 --> 03:10.060
[Lvwan Restaurant]

03:20.910 --> 03:22.070
Zhuge Yue,

03:22.490 --> 03:23.820
what are you doing here?

03:26.750 --> 03:27.590
Zhuge Huai,

03:28.400 --> 03:29.400
the fire from your Hongshan Manor

03:29.400 --> 03:31.470
has spread all the way
to my Qingshan Manor.

03:31.470 --> 03:33.120
Shouldn't you compensate for it?

03:33.120 --> 03:33.800
Why?

03:34.360 --> 03:36.240
Is your Qingshan Manor so poor

03:36.710 --> 03:39.260
that you need to settle accounts
for some shabby rooms?

03:39.260 --> 03:41.560
Qingshan Manor
has always had clear accounts,

03:41.560 --> 03:43.000
unlike your Hongshan Manor,

03:43.000 --> 03:44.590
which is a mess.

03:44.840 --> 03:46.310
You can't manage your people

03:46.310 --> 03:47.590
or settle accounts.

03:50.800 --> 03:51.630
Zhuge Yue,

03:52.360 --> 03:53.960
are you here to make fun of me?

03:55.400 --> 03:57.000
I have no time for such things.

03:57.000 --> 03:58.430
It's just that my Qingshan Manor

03:58.430 --> 04:00.520
can't suffer losses for no reason.

04:01.470 --> 04:02.730
Since you can't manage

04:03.080 --> 04:04.280
these female slaves,

04:04.430 --> 04:05.560
they are useless.

04:06.120 --> 04:09.180
Take them to the hunting ground
to feed the wild wolves.

04:09.750 --> 04:10.520
Why?

04:11.750 --> 04:12.810
Can't bear to do it?

04:18.149 --> 04:20.740
No wonder His Majesty values you.

04:21.070 --> 04:22.630
When it comes to ruthlessness,

04:22.630 --> 04:24.480
it has to be you, Zhuge Yue.

04:28.680 --> 04:29.540
Take them away.

05:01.190 --> 05:01.870
Go east,

05:02.870 --> 05:04.130
leave Zhenhuang City,

05:05.120 --> 05:06.250
and never come back.

05:06.630 --> 05:10.230
What are you waiting for?
Do you truly wish to be fed to the wolves?

05:14.950 --> 05:16.150
All of you, step down.

05:17.900 --> 05:18.820
You two as well.

05:32.150 --> 05:32.920
Come out.

05:33.360 --> 05:34.620
There are wolves here.

05:34.870 --> 05:36.130
You'll lose your life.

05:58.270 --> 05:59.950
With your poor martial arts,

06:00.390 --> 06:02.800
you still dared to break into
Hongshan Manor alone to save people?

06:02.800 --> 06:04.310
I'm afraid that if you
hadn't come to save her,

06:04.310 --> 06:05.370
your little sister

06:05.680 --> 06:07.480
could have lived a few more days.

06:11.150 --> 06:12.410
You were already dead.

06:12.520 --> 06:13.830
Don't think that because you
let everyone go,

06:13.830 --> 06:15.070
I will thank you.

06:15.560 --> 06:17.040
You and that Zhuge Huai

06:17.740 --> 06:19.000
are birds of a feather.

06:19.630 --> 06:21.890
Do you want to continue fighting with me,

06:22.330 --> 06:23.630
ending up dead at my hands,

06:23.630 --> 06:24.920
or do you want me to teach you

06:24.920 --> 06:27.310
how to survive

06:28.630 --> 06:30.490
in this cruel and ruthless world?

06:35.440 --> 06:36.440
It's up to you.

06:58.780 --> 07:01.240
King Ximeng only gave you
a 10-day antidote.

07:01.600 --> 07:03.860
I didn't expect you to hold out until now.

07:03.930 --> 07:05.590
I really underestimated you.

07:08.300 --> 07:09.040
Even if you hold on to

07:09.040 --> 07:11.160
the poison of Blood on Snow
for just a moment,

07:11.160 --> 07:12.240
next,

07:12.360 --> 07:14.240
you will be more painful,
a fate worse than death.

07:14.240 --> 07:14.950
Still hoping

07:14.950 --> 07:17.070
to run away with your beloved one?

07:17.330 --> 07:18.540
Dream on.

07:30.270 --> 07:30.870
Qiao,

07:31.160 --> 07:32.630
I can't reach the food on your side.

07:32.630 --> 07:33.890
Help me pass some tofu.

07:34.420 --> 07:35.500
This mutton looks really good.

07:35.500 --> 07:36.760
Have some more of this.

07:38.190 --> 07:40.790
If you don't eat this mutton,
it will get tough.

07:41.560 --> 07:43.690
You are a wanted criminal in Great Yan.

07:44.070 --> 07:45.950
How dare you invite me to eat hot pot

07:45.950 --> 07:47.390
within Great Yan's territory?

07:47.390 --> 07:48.800
If we don't eat today,

07:50.000 --> 07:51.200
after the big battle,

07:52.530 --> 07:53.990
there will be even less chance to eat.

07:53.990 --> 07:55.280
After this battle,

07:57.070 --> 07:59.130
I don't know how many innocent bodies

07:59.310 --> 08:01.960
will be covered under the heavy snow.

08:02.390 --> 08:03.040
Xing,

08:03.750 --> 08:05.880
have you ever regretted your choices?

08:08.680 --> 08:09.830
I have no regrets

08:10.390 --> 08:11.720
because I had no choice.

08:13.160 --> 08:14.890
I was born a slave of Great Yong,

08:15.480 --> 08:18.080
a worthless maid in Qingshan Manor.

08:18.990 --> 08:21.110
Whether I fight alongside Yan Xun

08:21.510 --> 08:23.640
or serve as a general of the Xiuli Army,

08:24.250 --> 08:24.840
you

08:25.920 --> 08:27.920
will always be on the opposite side.

08:28.310 --> 08:29.750
If you were just Xing,

08:29.750 --> 08:31.750
and I wasn't a general of Great Yong,

08:32.870 --> 08:34.470
could we leave here together

08:36.080 --> 08:38.390
and no longer bear those responsibilities

08:38.390 --> 08:39.549
and hatred?

08:43.700 --> 08:45.030
But we are not like that.

08:46.720 --> 08:48.270
I won't forget my name,

08:49.030 --> 08:50.230
and neither will you.

08:50.630 --> 08:52.870
You can never cast off the Zhuge name,

08:53.510 --> 08:56.040
and I can never let go
of my responsibilities.

08:56.080 --> 08:57.030
We are destined

08:58.390 --> 08:59.870
never to stand together.

09:05.370 --> 09:06.600
Come on, eat more.

09:06.790 --> 09:08.630
You need to be full
to have the strength to find Zhuge Yue.

09:08.630 --> 09:09.600
Slap him twice

09:09.600 --> 09:10.910
and kick him down!

09:16.950 --> 09:18.210
Here, dip some of this.

09:19.320 --> 09:20.000
Qiao,

09:20.270 --> 09:21.390
I have an idea.

09:21.790 --> 09:23.320
I'll go to the palace right now

09:23.320 --> 09:24.050
and tell them

09:24.150 --> 09:26.360
Zhuge Yue,
Chief of Great Yong's Qingshan Manor,

09:26.360 --> 09:27.220
is in Tangjing.

09:27.510 --> 09:29.300
I'll ask my mother
to order the entire Biantang

09:29.300 --> 09:31.200
to issue a warrant for Zhuge Yue's arrest.

09:31.200 --> 09:32.480
Before he runs far,

09:32.500 --> 09:34.100
we can definitely catch him.

09:34.440 --> 09:36.320
Who asked you to issue a warrant for him?

09:36.320 --> 09:37.850
Why do you want to catch him?

09:37.870 --> 09:39.480
Catch him to beat him up.

09:39.910 --> 09:42.170
Acting all solemn and playing dead, huh?

09:43.720 --> 09:46.080
With your slender waist and small figure,

09:46.670 --> 09:48.000
you can catch Zhuge Yue?

09:48.720 --> 09:49.510
Qiao.

09:50.720 --> 09:52.240
I'm trying to figure out
a way to vent your anger.

09:52.240 --> 09:53.970
Why do you still look down on me?

09:54.750 --> 09:55.870
But anyway,

09:56.150 --> 09:57.480
Zhuge Yue is still alive.

09:57.480 --> 09:59.080
He hasn't lost an arm or a leg.

09:59.200 --> 10:00.550
You've also recovered your eyesight,

10:00.550 --> 10:02.880
and you can still see his cold expression.

10:03.270 --> 10:05.840
Sometimes when you like someone,

10:06.240 --> 10:07.960
-as long as—
-Who said I like him?

10:07.960 --> 10:09.020
You don't like him?

10:10.840 --> 10:11.770
That was before.

10:12.720 --> 10:15.050
Now he doesn't recognize me and avoids me.

10:15.080 --> 10:16.550
He also broke his promise to me.

10:16.550 --> 10:18.600
I might have to reconsider this.

10:22.440 --> 10:22.870
Li Ce,

10:23.160 --> 10:24.070
don't worry.

10:24.910 --> 10:26.150
I will live well.

10:30.380 --> 10:31.120
Qiao.

10:31.720 --> 10:33.080
Then consider me.

10:33.960 --> 10:35.550
I'm way better than Zhuge Yue

10:35.550 --> 10:36.630
and his cold expression.

10:36.630 --> 10:38.840
I'm handsome, suave,

10:39.220 --> 10:41.620
elegant, and talented.

10:52.810 --> 10:54.070
Straighten your back!

10:54.960 --> 10:55.720
Hurry up!

10:56.440 --> 10:56.970
Hurry up!

10:59.360 --> 11:01.270
Get up! Get up!

11:03.450 --> 11:04.100
Speed up!

11:07.440 --> 11:07.960
Up.

11:08.390 --> 11:09.080
Hurry up.

11:42.910 --> 11:44.280
Greetings, Your Majesty.

11:44.280 --> 11:46.150
Congratulations
on being under the protection of the gods

11:46.150 --> 11:47.750
and surviving the disaster.

11:47.800 --> 11:48.960
General Huan,

11:49.590 --> 11:51.250
you've worked hard recently.

11:53.190 --> 11:53.980
I am guilty.

11:54.240 --> 11:56.020
You quelled the internal rebellion

11:56.020 --> 11:58.350
and stabilized the Great Yan army morale.

11:58.510 --> 12:00.240
What crime have you committed?

12:02.440 --> 12:04.270
I privately commanded the whole army

12:04.270 --> 12:06.150
and dispatched the Yan Army
and the Black Eagle Army together

12:06.150 --> 12:08.410
to suppress Katuo's tribe's rebellion.

12:09.030 --> 12:10.240
But if I had done nothing,

12:10.240 --> 12:13.440
I'm afraid Great Yan
would have undergone a great change.

12:19.270 --> 12:21.070
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

12:23.940 --> 12:26.720
General Huan, you're tired
from suppressing the rebellion.

12:26.720 --> 12:28.240
Go back and rest.

12:29.280 --> 12:32.610
The soldiers of the Snowy Region Tribe
and the border troops

12:33.140 --> 12:36.140
are also looking forward to
your return day and night.

12:36.720 --> 12:38.120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

14:01.030 --> 14:04.200
The dignified Black Eagle Army
should be open and aboveboard.

14:04.200 --> 14:05.630
Yet you hide your heads
and show your tails,

14:05.630 --> 14:06.640
shameless.

14:06.670 --> 14:07.470
General Huan,

14:08.510 --> 14:10.030
we are also acting under orders.

14:10.030 --> 14:11.360
Since you are courting death,

14:11.360 --> 14:12.870
I will grant your wish.

14:43.720 --> 14:44.630
Your Majesty,

14:45.440 --> 14:46.510
the whole of Great Yan

14:46.510 --> 14:48.150
knows that the black eagles

14:48.630 --> 14:50.230
brought you back from death,

14:50.320 --> 14:52.550
and that the gods

14:52.550 --> 14:53.480
of Mount Hei

14:54.390 --> 14:56.770
protect the ruler of Great Yan.

15:02.080 --> 15:03.080
From now on,

15:03.390 --> 15:05.630
even the tribal elders of Great Yan

15:06.840 --> 15:08.200
won't dare to

15:09.080 --> 15:11.200
have any disloyalty

15:11.870 --> 15:13.800
toward you, the ruler of Great Yan.

15:23.750 --> 15:26.360
Your medicine is quite useful.

15:27.270 --> 15:28.870
Thank you, Your Majesty.

15:29.290 --> 15:30.410
I just used

15:30.440 --> 15:32.240
some herbs that attract beasts.

15:33.120 --> 15:34.790
It's just a small trick.

15:42.870 --> 15:43.670
Your Majesty.

15:44.120 --> 15:46.870
I laid an ambush along the road
to intercept General Huan,

15:46.870 --> 15:49.680
but she fought with all her might.

15:50.840 --> 15:51.440
She...

15:52.120 --> 15:52.980
What happened?

15:54.200 --> 15:56.270
She escaped, and her fate is unknown.

16:21.340 --> 16:22.550
You saved my life

16:23.900 --> 16:25.930
and put on such a great show with me.

16:26.550 --> 16:28.270
I will reward you handsomely.

16:29.870 --> 16:31.360
Thank you, Your Majesty.

16:50.030 --> 16:51.270
Why?

17:12.200 --> 17:13.440
Only if you die

17:14.550 --> 17:17.109
can I truly become the ruler of Great Yan,

17:17.680 --> 17:19.240
who were resurrected

17:22.349 --> 17:24.349
by the gods of Mount Hei.

17:31.110 --> 17:31.910
General Huan?

17:32.310 --> 17:34.200
Why would General Huan
be treated like this?

17:34.200 --> 17:36.510
His Majesty is the ruler of Great Yan,
protected by the gods of Mount Hei.

17:36.510 --> 17:38.160
General Huan overstepped her authority

17:38.160 --> 17:40.550
and seized military power
while His Majesty was in a coma.

17:40.550 --> 17:42.880
This is His Majesty's punishment for her.

17:48.880 --> 17:50.720
General Huan disobeyed the King's orders,

17:50.720 --> 17:53.780
privately mobilized troops,
and rebelled against the decree.

17:53.780 --> 17:55.510
During the turmoil in Great Yan,

17:55.510 --> 17:56.740
she fought for her own selfish interests.

17:56.740 --> 17:59.350
She was executed today,
but her crimes are unforgivable.

17:59.350 --> 18:02.270
Her corpse will be exposed
for 3 days as a warning to others.

18:02.270 --> 18:03.200
From now on,

18:04.530 --> 18:06.960
gather strong soldiers
and brave generals from all tribes

18:06.960 --> 18:08.620
to flatten Great Yong with me!

18:09.240 --> 18:12.700
-As you command, Your Majesty!
-As you command, Your Majesty!

18:30.620 --> 18:32.680
[Ximeng City]

19:02.370 --> 19:03.370
Zhuge Yue,

19:03.870 --> 19:06.450
you broke your promise
and tried to walk away.

19:06.480 --> 19:07.440
I thought you

19:07.440 --> 19:10.370
could really withstand
the torture of Blood on Snow.

19:10.640 --> 19:14.440
I am already living like a ghost.

19:15.610 --> 19:17.410
What does it matter if I die?

19:17.780 --> 19:20.350
Your martial arts
helped you survive this many days,

19:20.350 --> 19:22.360
which is quite surprising to me.

19:22.980 --> 19:25.130
So I won't let you die.

19:25.460 --> 19:26.940
I need

19:27.550 --> 19:29.350
capable slaves.

19:46.960 --> 19:49.110
I'll give you another chance.

19:49.510 --> 19:51.400
This is the 10-day dose.

19:51.550 --> 19:52.750
In exchange,

19:53.160 --> 19:55.880
you have to do something for me.

19:56.480 --> 19:56.890
What

19:57.240 --> 19:58.300
do you want me to do?

19:58.510 --> 20:00.510
From now on,

20:01.640 --> 20:04.310
you are not only my slave

20:04.720 --> 20:06.550
but also

20:06.960 --> 20:08.110
my shadow.

20:29.420 --> 20:31.060
[Boque Palace]

21:56.400 --> 21:59.030
Are you sure it was a woman
who entered your room?

21:59.030 --> 21:59.960
I can't be wrong.

22:00.590 --> 22:02.110
She must have come to spy.

22:03.150 --> 22:05.400
She opened the secret compartment
under my bed.

22:05.400 --> 22:07.200
The flag of the Xiuli Army is in it.

22:07.200 --> 22:09.030
I have 14 concubines and maids

22:09.680 --> 22:11.000
in my mansion,

22:11.000 --> 22:12.240
all nominally granted by the Empress.

22:12.240 --> 22:12.880
But it's also possible

22:12.880 --> 22:15.480
that Zhan Ziyu secretly planted
someone among them.

22:15.480 --> 22:18.070
It's hard to investigate
with just this information.

22:18.070 --> 22:19.730
Are there any other features?

22:23.480 --> 22:24.310
Let me think.

22:25.750 --> 22:26.750
She is quite thin.

22:27.590 --> 22:28.400
She should be

22:28.400 --> 22:30.510
between an inch or two shorter than me.

22:30.510 --> 22:32.350
But unlike Linlang and the others,

22:32.350 --> 22:33.550
her strike is powerful.

22:33.550 --> 22:34.930
She must have practiced
martial arts since childhood.

22:34.930 --> 22:35.790
One more thing.

22:36.680 --> 22:38.740
Her martial arts look familiar to me,

22:38.750 --> 22:40.590
but I don't completely recognize them.

22:40.590 --> 22:41.790
What about her scent?

22:42.160 --> 22:43.760
Was she wearing any perfume?

22:43.960 --> 22:45.020
Since it's a woman,

22:45.400 --> 22:47.000
was she wearing any jewelry?

22:47.440 --> 22:48.240
None of those.

22:52.310 --> 22:53.170
Your Highness.

22:53.270 --> 22:54.810
Lord Zhan just passed on
an oral edict from the Empress,

22:54.810 --> 22:56.550
saying she heard
Princess Fu has been found

22:56.550 --> 22:57.350
and requests you

22:57.350 --> 23:00.550
to bring Princess Fu
to the palace for a talk immediately.

23:03.920 --> 23:05.790
When we enter the hall later,
just wait on the side.

23:05.790 --> 23:07.050
I'll deal with Mother.

23:18.720 --> 23:20.850
I pay my respects to you, Your Majesty.

23:21.960 --> 23:23.760
I pay my respects to you, Mother.

23:25.970 --> 23:27.790
Fu, you've been away for many years.

23:27.790 --> 23:29.720
A girl changes a lot as she grows up.

23:30.270 --> 23:32.130
I almost couldn't recognize you.

23:40.510 --> 23:41.240
You may rise.

23:42.520 --> 23:45.120
-Thank you, Mother.
-Thank you, Your Majesty.

23:45.910 --> 23:49.110
You indeed look quite different
from when you were a child.

23:49.110 --> 23:51.510
These eyebrows and eyes

23:51.510 --> 23:52.880
and this thin figure

23:52.900 --> 23:54.530
do look somewhat similar.

23:54.850 --> 23:55.650
However...

23:56.790 --> 23:58.310
you don't seem like Fu.

24:02.190 --> 24:03.510
You look a bit like...

24:04.830 --> 24:08.160
the escaped slave
Great Yan and Great Yong are hunting down,

24:08.160 --> 24:09.110
Chu Qiao.

24:18.370 --> 24:19.290
Your Majesty,

24:20.010 --> 24:21.470
who are you talking about?

24:23.640 --> 24:26.440
Chu Qiao was a female slave of Great Yong,

24:26.800 --> 24:29.510
who later, surprisingly,
became a female general of Great Yan.

24:29.510 --> 24:30.850
Now both Great Yan and Great Yong

24:30.850 --> 24:32.590
are hunting for her everywhere,

24:32.590 --> 24:34.110
causing a huge uproar.

24:34.680 --> 24:37.070
Even our Biantang has no peace.

24:37.680 --> 24:38.240
Ce,

24:38.890 --> 24:40.350
when you were in Great Yong,

24:40.350 --> 24:42.550
didn't you say
you wanted to marry Chu Qiao?

24:42.550 --> 24:44.040
Look closely at her.

24:44.490 --> 24:46.490
Doesn't she look a lot like Chu Qiao?

24:48.350 --> 24:49.720
You must be joking, Mother.

24:49.720 --> 24:51.720
How could Fu and Chu Qiao look alike?

24:52.250 --> 24:53.250
Your Majesty.

24:54.090 --> 24:55.750
When I was wandering outside,

24:55.940 --> 24:58.770
I heard that the Crown Prince of Biantang
went to Great Yong as an envoy

24:58.770 --> 25:01.190
to marry a female martial arts instructor
of the imperial guard.

25:01.190 --> 25:02.520
I wonder, Your Majesty,

25:02.740 --> 25:04.550
if you're talking about that Chu Qiao.

25:04.550 --> 25:05.200
Fu,

25:05.880 --> 25:06.740
don't be angry.

25:06.880 --> 25:08.170
The reason I wanted to marry her back then

25:08.170 --> 25:10.160
was that she looked somewhat like you.

25:10.160 --> 25:11.960
And I thought you had already...

25:12.840 --> 25:14.350
You can't blame me for this.

25:14.350 --> 25:17.280
Mother, please don't mention
the past in front of Fu.

25:17.680 --> 25:19.540
Since you say you are Princess Fu,

25:19.720 --> 25:20.720
let me ask you,

25:20.860 --> 25:24.060
do you remember how old you were
when you came to Biantang?

25:24.250 --> 25:25.200
When I was 6,

25:25.820 --> 25:28.080
His Majesty granted my father
the title of Prince of Pingnan

25:28.080 --> 25:29.810
and my mother the title of Lady Dingguo,

25:29.810 --> 25:32.470
as well as the Prince of Pingnan's Mansion
in the west of the city.

25:32.470 --> 25:34.350
I then followed my father and mother

25:34.350 --> 25:35.590
to Tangjing.

25:35.920 --> 25:37.590
Who on earth is Princess Fu?

25:37.590 --> 25:38.640
Fu's father

25:39.310 --> 25:40.770
was the Prince of Pingnan.

25:40.960 --> 25:41.590
Her mother

25:42.320 --> 25:43.480
was Lady Dingguo.

25:43.510 --> 25:44.960
Then do you remember me?

25:45.200 --> 25:47.070
I remember seeing you 3 times.

25:47.830 --> 25:49.790
Once at His Majesty's birthday banquet,

25:49.790 --> 25:52.250
once when praying to Heaven
for the Empress,

25:52.340 --> 25:54.970
and another time
at the Crown Prince's birthday.

25:54.970 --> 25:56.430
But I only saw you from afar

25:56.960 --> 25:59.200
and didn't have the chance
to get close to you.

25:59.200 --> 26:00.270
My mother once said

26:00.590 --> 26:02.210
that you and she were close friends

26:02.210 --> 26:03.440
before you both got married.

26:03.440 --> 26:04.330
However,

26:04.750 --> 26:06.680
after she married Fu's father,

26:07.020 --> 26:08.620
she moved away from Tangjing

26:08.920 --> 26:11.680
and gradually grew distant from my mother.

26:14.000 --> 26:14.680
Mother,

26:15.190 --> 26:17.150
why do you suspect that she is not Fu,

26:17.150 --> 26:18.150
but Chu Qiao?

26:19.860 --> 26:20.410
Ce,

26:20.940 --> 26:22.640
don't blame me for being suspicious.

26:22.640 --> 26:24.700
This is a matter of great importance.

26:24.880 --> 26:26.140
It happened suddenly.

26:26.720 --> 26:27.960
I must figure it out.

26:30.070 --> 26:31.310
I deeply appreciate

26:31.480 --> 26:33.000
your good intentions, Mother.

26:33.000 --> 26:33.680
However,

26:34.480 --> 26:36.480
Princess Fu has not fully recovered

26:36.490 --> 26:38.070
and has been exhausted for half a day.

26:38.070 --> 26:39.530
If you have no more doubts,

26:39.790 --> 26:41.510
why not let me take her back

26:41.660 --> 26:42.660
to rest early?

26:43.880 --> 26:44.480
All right.

26:45.200 --> 26:46.070
Then today,

26:46.550 --> 26:47.880
you may take your leave.

26:49.780 --> 26:52.380
-Thank you, Mother.
-Thank you, Your Majesty.

27:02.270 --> 27:03.070
Your Majesty,

27:03.160 --> 27:04.690
I can guarantee with my life

27:04.920 --> 27:05.830
that the woman

27:05.830 --> 27:07.290
His Highness brought back

27:07.720 --> 27:09.520
is the general of the Xiuli Army,

27:09.830 --> 27:10.640
Chu Qiao.

27:11.250 --> 27:12.010
Lord Zhao,

27:12.910 --> 27:14.980
it's not that I don't believe
what you said.

27:14.980 --> 27:16.610
It's just that I have never seen

27:16.610 --> 27:18.890
the famous Chu Qiao,

27:19.130 --> 27:21.460
and this is the first time
I've met you too.

27:21.980 --> 27:22.740
But I

27:22.760 --> 27:24.860
did see Princess Fu when she was young.

27:24.860 --> 27:27.060
The woman the Crown Prince brought back

27:27.160 --> 27:29.960
does resemble Princess Fu.

27:30.350 --> 27:31.150
Your Majesty,

27:31.230 --> 27:32.740
I was once a trusted advisor

27:32.740 --> 27:34.680
to a noble family of Great Yong,
the Muhe family.

27:34.680 --> 27:36.350
I have seen Chu Qiao many times.

27:36.350 --> 27:38.160
After the Jiuyou Platform accident,
Yan Xun was imprisoned.

27:38.160 --> 27:39.640
Young Master Muhe Xifeng and I

27:39.640 --> 27:41.000
once went to the prison.

27:41.030 --> 27:43.200
Yan Xun was highly protective of Chu Qiao,

27:43.200 --> 27:45.090
even cutting off one of his own fingers.

27:45.090 --> 27:46.690
I was at the scene at the time.

27:47.000 --> 27:47.910
After this,

27:48.240 --> 27:49.160
Yan Xun and Chu Qiao

27:49.160 --> 27:50.720
hate Lord Muhe to the bone.

27:51.110 --> 27:52.920
They plotted to kill him.

27:53.510 --> 27:55.830
Whether this is true or false,

27:56.310 --> 27:59.170
you can find out
by sending someone to investigate.

28:00.720 --> 28:01.780
From what you said,

28:02.320 --> 28:03.850
it doesn't seem to be false.

28:07.690 --> 28:08.370
Lord Zhao,

28:08.850 --> 28:10.050
please go back first.

28:10.720 --> 28:12.310
I will take my leave.

28:19.550 --> 28:20.350
Your Majesty,

28:20.640 --> 28:22.150
but now the Crown Prince insists

28:22.150 --> 28:23.480
that she is Princess Fu.

28:23.750 --> 28:26.070
We can't find any flaws
for the time being.

28:26.070 --> 28:27.530
Then keep a close eye on her

28:27.610 --> 28:29.010
and the Crown Prince's Mansion.

28:29.010 --> 28:30.160
I'd like to see

28:30.310 --> 28:32.750
what the Crown Prince
can possibly accomplish

28:32.750 --> 28:35.010
with this fake princess he brought back.

28:35.310 --> 28:35.880
Yes.

28:39.830 --> 28:40.480
By the way,

28:41.550 --> 28:43.830
the Prince of Luo
has completed his 3 years of mourning.

28:43.830 --> 28:44.960
By my calculations,

28:45.270 --> 28:47.160
he should be on his way back now.

28:48.690 --> 28:49.690
I understand.

28:50.510 --> 28:53.640
I will go and welcome
the Prince of Luo back to the palace.

29:18.680 --> 29:19.750
Your Highness.

29:22.510 --> 29:24.740
Her Majesty knows
your mourning period is over.

29:24.740 --> 29:26.450
She sent us to wait here

29:26.830 --> 29:28.450
and welcome you
into the palace for a chat.

29:28.450 --> 29:31.270
Why does Her Majesty
summon me to the palace so suddenly?

29:31.270 --> 29:33.200
Can you tell me in advance, My Lord?

29:33.550 --> 29:35.750
You will know once you enter the palace.

29:39.030 --> 29:40.230
Please wait a moment.

29:45.590 --> 29:46.120
Chun'er.

29:48.240 --> 29:49.000
Chun'er.

29:49.750 --> 29:51.030
I have something to attend to.

29:51.030 --> 29:51.640
Li Yan,

29:52.030 --> 29:53.160
who exactly are you?

29:53.400 --> 29:56.000
Why would the Empress
summon you to the palace?

30:00.030 --> 30:00.680
Who is he?

30:00.790 --> 30:02.140
You go back to the mansion first.

30:02.140 --> 30:04.740
I will explain everything
to you when I return.

30:18.120 --> 30:18.960
Your Highness.

30:18.960 --> 30:20.270
An imperial edict has come
from Her Majesty in the palace.

30:20.270 --> 30:22.250
It says it's a joyous occasion
that Princess Fu has been found,

30:22.250 --> 30:23.480
so a banquet will be held in the palace.

30:23.480 --> 30:24.920
Princess Fu is invited
to enter the palace immediately.

30:24.920 --> 30:25.750
Immediately?

30:26.130 --> 30:26.930
Immediately.

30:43.480 --> 30:44.080
Remember,

30:44.750 --> 30:46.110
your mother was an only child,

30:46.110 --> 30:47.730
and your parents have passed away.

30:47.730 --> 30:48.930
Even if there are kin in the family,

30:48.930 --> 30:49.900
none of them have seen you before.

30:49.900 --> 30:51.720
They won't be able to tell
if you're Princess Fu.

30:51.720 --> 30:53.640
The Prince of Pingnan
was not from Tangjing,

30:53.640 --> 30:55.770
and his relatives aren't here either.

30:55.960 --> 30:57.290
No matter what they say,

30:57.680 --> 30:58.810
don't believe them.

31:02.400 --> 31:06.200
The Princess Consort of Pingnan and I
used to be like sisters.

31:07.070 --> 31:10.840
The Prince of Pingnan died for his country
on a battlefield thousands of miles away.

31:10.840 --> 31:12.200
I originally thought

31:12.220 --> 31:16.350
the Princess Consort of Pingnan
and Princess Fu had tragically perished.

31:16.350 --> 31:18.820
I didn't expect Princess Fu
to be blessed by heaven.

31:18.820 --> 31:20.650
I am happy for Princess Fu.

31:20.880 --> 31:23.400
Today, I have invited an old friend

31:23.790 --> 31:25.390
especially for Princess Fu.

31:42.290 --> 31:43.690
I am Prince of Luo, Li Yan.

31:43.720 --> 31:45.850
I pay my respects to you, Your Majesty.

31:51.980 --> 31:52.830
Princess Fu.

31:53.890 --> 31:57.090
You couldn't have forgotten
the Prince of Luo, could you?

31:57.200 --> 31:59.680
He is your childhood sweetheart,

32:00.030 --> 32:01.720
your betrothed husband.

32:02.270 --> 32:05.240
He is most familiar
with your looks and habits.

32:06.060 --> 32:07.570
Others might mistake you,

32:07.880 --> 32:08.400
but he

32:08.790 --> 32:10.240
definitely won't.

32:13.200 --> 32:14.000
Prince of Luo.

32:14.880 --> 32:16.900
Since your marriage to Princess Fu
was arranged by your parents,

32:16.900 --> 32:18.620
there's no need for formalities.

32:18.620 --> 32:20.380
Go and sit next to Princess Fu.

32:20.750 --> 32:22.270
After the banquet,

32:22.640 --> 32:25.680
I will have the Ministry of Rites
choose an auspicious day

32:25.680 --> 32:27.400
for your wedding.

32:44.790 --> 32:45.590
Prince of Luo.

32:46.550 --> 32:47.510
What's wrong?

32:48.350 --> 32:50.400
You haven't seen Princess Fu
for a long time.

32:50.400 --> 32:51.750
Aren't you happy?

32:52.400 --> 32:54.060
Or is the person in front of you

32:54.350 --> 32:56.350
not Princess Fu at all?

32:57.590 --> 32:58.390
Prince of Luo,

32:58.550 --> 32:59.440
answer me.

33:00.070 --> 33:01.640
Is the woman in front of you

33:02.400 --> 33:04.200
Princess Fu?

33:19.400 --> 33:20.550
Your Majesty,

33:21.030 --> 33:22.880
I haven't seen Princess Fu in years.

33:22.880 --> 33:25.130
It is inevitable that appearances change.

33:25.130 --> 33:26.060
Perhaps Your Majesty,

33:26.060 --> 33:28.990
you could allow Princess Fu
and me to talk in private.

33:34.070 --> 33:35.000
Your Highness.

33:35.830 --> 33:37.160
I don't know who you are,

33:37.480 --> 33:39.680
but you're definitely not Princess Fu.

33:42.310 --> 33:43.240
What do you want?

33:44.270 --> 33:45.960
It's easy for you to kill me now,

33:45.960 --> 33:47.490
but you'll implicate Li Ce,

33:48.350 --> 33:50.550
and you won't walk out of the palace
alive yourself.

33:50.550 --> 33:52.410
I want you to go out now and confirm

33:53.000 --> 33:54.350
that I am Princess Fu.

33:54.400 --> 33:55.030
Saving me

33:55.900 --> 33:57.030
is also saving Li Ce.

33:57.880 --> 33:59.080
I'm right behind you.

33:59.200 --> 34:00.600
If you say one wrong word,

34:00.830 --> 34:02.830
I'll kill you on the spot.

34:06.790 --> 34:08.190
Answer me 3 questions.

34:08.230 --> 34:09.290
If you answer them,

34:09.800 --> 34:10.929
I'll go out with you.

34:17.840 --> 34:18.400
Speak.

34:18.840 --> 34:19.770
First question.

34:20.840 --> 34:21.969
Who exactly are you?

34:22.670 --> 34:24.840
Although you look a bit like Fu,

34:25.110 --> 34:26.989
which made me almost
get the wrong person just now,

34:26.989 --> 34:27.949
you are not her.

34:29.070 --> 34:30.320
Fu is dead.

34:31.360 --> 34:32.489
Who exactly are you?

34:32.710 --> 34:34.030
I am not from Biantang.

34:34.909 --> 34:36.040
I am from Great Yong.

34:36.360 --> 34:37.400
I was a slave.

34:37.800 --> 34:39.969
When Li Ce went to Zhenhuang City
as an envoy,

34:39.969 --> 34:41.120
we met there.

34:41.139 --> 34:41.830
Alright.

34:42.510 --> 34:43.630
Second question.

34:43.880 --> 34:45.940
Why did you pretend to be Princess Fu?

34:46.190 --> 34:47.850
And what is your purpose here?

34:47.920 --> 34:48.800
Because of me,

34:49.510 --> 34:50.770
many things happened,

34:51.510 --> 34:53.370
and many people were implicated.

34:53.620 --> 34:56.550
Now Great Yan and Great Yong
are both hunting me down.

34:56.810 --> 34:57.730
To save me,

34:57.920 --> 34:59.680
Li Ce brought me back from Great Yan.

34:59.680 --> 35:02.480
In desperation, he lied
and said I was Princess Fu.

35:02.580 --> 35:04.240
I don't care about my own life.

35:04.280 --> 35:05.370
But Li Ce

35:05.880 --> 35:07.230
took a great risk for me.

35:07.590 --> 35:08.710
I don't want him

35:09.480 --> 35:11.030
to get hurt because of me again.

35:11.030 --> 35:13.150
What is the third question?

35:13.630 --> 35:14.670
It

35:15.440 --> 35:16.760
is a deal.

35:17.550 --> 35:19.440
I want you to promise me one thing.

35:31.230 --> 35:32.030
Your Majesty,

35:32.920 --> 35:34.180
the woman in front of us

35:34.550 --> 35:37.480
is indeed Princess Fu
who has been missing for years.

35:41.450 --> 35:42.810
Princess Fu's return

35:42.840 --> 35:44.440
is truly a joyous occasion.

35:44.760 --> 35:47.000
But Princess Fu and I
haven't seen each other for years,

35:47.000 --> 35:48.330
and we have grown apart.

35:48.480 --> 35:50.080
Getting married at this time

35:50.110 --> 35:51.770
might be a bit inappropriate.

35:51.800 --> 35:53.960
I appreciate your kindness, Your Majesty.

35:53.960 --> 35:55.710
I sincerely ask for your permission

35:55.710 --> 35:58.190
to postpone the wedding.

36:00.960 --> 36:02.550
I heard that since Princess Fu returned,

36:02.550 --> 36:05.380
she's been at the Crown Prince's Mansion
under your care, Your Highness.

36:05.380 --> 36:07.900
I thank you for that.

36:11.190 --> 36:11.880
Li Ce.

36:12.880 --> 36:14.510
There is something I've never figured out.

36:14.510 --> 36:16.880
Aren't you the legitimate Crown Prince
born to the Biantang Empress?

36:16.880 --> 36:18.280
Why is she so wary of you?

36:20.480 --> 36:21.610
In the royal family,

36:21.940 --> 36:24.070
blood ties are the most useless thing.

36:24.920 --> 36:26.760
In order to fight for the heir apparent,

36:26.760 --> 36:29.480
my father killed his own elder brother,
Crown Prince Maocheng.

36:29.480 --> 36:31.920
He placed Crown Prince Maocheng's
full brother, Prince of Chang,

36:31.920 --> 36:33.660
under house arrest in the remote Jincheng.

36:33.660 --> 36:35.000
The Prince of Luo, Li Yan,

36:35.000 --> 36:37.440
is the only surviving bloodline
of the late Prince of Chang.

36:37.440 --> 36:39.100
So, although the Prince of Luo

36:39.230 --> 36:40.590
holds the title,

36:41.030 --> 36:42.880
he's the descendant of a condemned prince.

36:42.880 --> 36:43.400
Yes.

36:44.960 --> 36:45.800
My mother

36:46.590 --> 36:48.630
is a woman of courage and vision.

36:49.400 --> 36:52.400
But she's far colder about feelings
than most people.

36:53.180 --> 36:54.640
I was raised by a wet nurse.

36:55.110 --> 36:56.040
When I was young,

36:56.840 --> 36:58.440
every time I tried to hug her,

36:58.630 --> 37:00.550
I would be coldly pushed away by her.

37:00.550 --> 37:01.440
Growing up,

37:01.960 --> 37:03.490
I found that compared to me,

37:03.550 --> 37:05.590
she seemed more interested in power.

37:05.590 --> 37:07.650
The further away I stayed from power,

37:07.680 --> 37:09.720
the more pleasant she would be to me.

37:10.550 --> 37:11.630
So all these years,

37:12.070 --> 37:15.330
I have been playing the role
of a playboy and a spendthrift.

37:16.550 --> 37:18.550
They're just a few beautiful spies.

37:18.960 --> 37:21.440
I have dealt with countless ruthless spies
in Qingshan Manor

37:21.440 --> 37:23.070
who wanted me dead.

37:24.590 --> 37:25.190
Li Ce,

37:25.880 --> 37:26.610
don't worry.

37:26.840 --> 37:28.040
Once my arm recovers,

37:28.150 --> 37:29.580
not only will I protect you,

37:29.580 --> 37:33.180
but I will also help you
take back everything that belongs to you.

37:52.920 --> 37:53.800
King Ximeng,

37:54.280 --> 37:56.800
Li'an City
will be your burial place today!

37:56.960 --> 37:57.360
She

37:57.590 --> 37:58.550
must die!

37:58.630 --> 37:59.670
Help!

38:00.880 --> 38:02.920
You are the Prince of Luo of Biantang,
a noble of the royal clan.

38:02.920 --> 38:03.400
No!

38:03.590 --> 38:04.280
No!

38:06.400 --> 38:07.070
Zhuge Yue,

38:07.510 --> 38:08.590
you must survive.

38:09.580 --> 38:10.660
Break the ice open.

38:10.920 --> 38:12.440
You must find the person for me!
